%% Vehicle status — from app/models/enums.py::VehicleStatus
%% No transition guard exists in code yet; this is the PROPOSED machine to
%% formalize in Phase 4 (ADR-ready). active is the only assignable state.
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> active : vehicle onboarded
    active --> maintenance : scheduled / breakdown
    maintenance --> active : service complete
    active --> decommissioned : retired
    maintenance --> decommissioned : write-off
    decommissioned --> [*]

    note right of active
      Only ACTIVE vehicles pass _validate_vehicle()
      in shipment_service.assign_driver_and_vehicle().
    end note
